00:01:10.470 --> 00:01:14.130
And I'm Vietnamese by heritage.

00:01:14.130 --> 00:01:15.660
I was born in Vietnam.

00:01:15.660 --> 00:01:19.830
And when my family
fled Vietnam in 1975,

00:01:19.830 --> 00:01:23.340
