00:03:29.850 --> 00:03:32.670
And what it offers are
different ways to make pho.

00:03:32.670 --> 00:03:35.820
So you can spend as
little as 40 minutes

00:03:35.820 --> 00:03:38.520
doctoring up canned broth.

00:03:38.520 --> 00:03:45.300
So if you could do me a favor
and hand me that can of broth--

