this is audience
participation time.

00:03:48.540 --> 00:03:50.425
And I'm not doing any
product placement.

00:03:50.425 --> 00:03:51.300
But stuff like this--

00:03:51.300 --> 00:03:53.040
Swanson's chicken broth.

00:03:53.040 --> 00:03:55.890
Or if you're shopping at
Whole Foods, then by all

00:03:55.890 --> 00:03:59.130
